{"data":[{"name":"107:1","price":"(ऐ नबी!) क्या आपने उसे देखा, जो बदले के दिन को झुठलाता है?","arabic":"أَرَءَيۡتَ ٱلَّذِي يُكَذِّبُ بِٱلدِّينِ","category":["107 (Al-Ma'un)","Al-Ma'un","Surah Al-Ma'un"],"ayahNumber":6198,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"hi","meta":{"transliteration":"ara-ayta alladhī yukadhibu bil-dīni ","translations":["Have you seen","the one who","denies","the Judgment","(1)"],"transliterationArr":["ara-ayta","alladhī","yukadhibu","bil-dīni",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1010],[2,1010,1670],[3,1670,2990],[4,2990,6185]]}},{"name":"107:2","price":"तो यही है, जो अनाथ (यतीम) को धक्के देता है।","arabic":"فَذَٰلِكَ ٱلَّذِي يَدُعُّ ٱلۡيَتِيمَ","category":["107 (Al-Ma'un)","Al-Ma'un","Surah Al-Ma'un"],"ayahNumber":6199,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"hi","meta":{"transliteration":"fadhālika alladhī yaduʿʿu al-yatīma ","translations":["Then that","(is) the one who","repulses","the orphan","(2)"],"transliterationArr":["fadhālika","alladhī","yaduʿʿu","al-yatīma",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1150],[2,1150,2000],[3,2000,2770],[4,2770,6435]]}},{"name":"107:3","price":"तथा ग़रीब को खाना खिलाने के लिए प्रोत्साहित नहीं करता है।[1]","arabic":"وَلَا يَحُضُّ عَلَىٰ طَعَامِ ٱلۡمِسۡكِينِ","category":["107 (Al-Ma'un)","Al-Ma'un","Surah Al-Ma'un"],"ayahNumber":6200,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"1. (2-3) इन आयतों में उन काफ़िरों (अधर्मियों) की दशा बताई गई है जो परलोक का इनकार करते थे।","lang":"hi","meta":{"transliteration":"walā yaḥuḍḍu ʿalā ṭaʿāmi al-mis'kīni ","translations":["And (does) not","feel the urge","to","feed","the poor","(3)"],"transliterationArr":["walā","yaḥuḍḍu","ʿalā","ṭaʿāmi","al-mis'kīni",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,760],[2,760,1730],[3,1730,2240],[4,2240,3150],[5,3150,7145]]}},{"name":"107:4","price":"तो विनाश है उन नमाज़ियों के लिए,[2]","arabic":"فَوَيۡلٞ لِّلۡمُصَلِّينَ","category":["107 (Al-Ma'un)","Al-Ma'un","Surah Al-Ma'un"],"ayahNumber":6201,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"2. इन आयतों में उन मुनाफ़िक़ों की दशा का वर्णन किया गया है, जो ऊपर से मुसलमान हैं परंतु उनके दिलों में परलोक और प्रतिकार का विश्वास नहीं है। इन दोनों प्रकारों के आचरण और स्वभाव को बयान करने से अभिप्राय यह बताना है कि इनसान में सदाचार की भावना परलोक पर विश्वास के बिना उत्पन्न नहीं हो सकती। और इस्लाम परलोक का सह़ीह विश्वास देकर इनसानों में अनाथों और ग़रीबों की सहायता की भावना पैदा करता है और उसे उदार तथा परोपकारी बनाता है।","lang":"hi","meta":{"transliteration":"fawaylun lil'muṣallīna ","translations":["So woe","to those who pray","(4)"],"transliterationArr":["fawaylun","lil'muṣallīna",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,930],[2,930,5365]]}},{"name":"107:5","price":"जो अपनी नमाज़ से लापरवाह हैं।","arabic":"ٱلَّذِينَ هُمۡ عَن صَلَاتِهِمۡ سَاهُونَ","category":["107 (Al-Ma'un)","Al-Ma'un","Surah Al-Ma'un"],"ayahNumber":6202,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"hi","meta":{"transliteration":"alladhīna hum ʿan ṣalātihim sāhūna ","translations":["Those who","[they]","about","their prayers","(are) neglectful","(5)"],"transliterationArr":["alladhīna","hum","ʿan","ṣalātihim","sāhūna",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1290],[2,1290,1680],[3,1680,2430],[4,2430,4090],[5,4090,7475]]}},{"name":"107:6","price":"वे जो दिखावा करते हैं।","arabic":"ٱلَّذِينَ هُمۡ يُرَآءُونَ","category":["107 (Al-Ma'un)","Al-Ma'un","Surah Al-Ma'un"],"ayahNumber":6203,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"hi","meta":{"transliteration":"alladhīna hum yurāūna ","translations":["Those who","[they]","make show","(6)"],"transliterationArr":["alladhīna","hum","yurāūna",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1230],[2,1230,1690],[3,1690,7455]]}},{"name":"107:7","price":"तथा साधारण बरतने की चीज़ भी माँगने से नहीं देते।[3]","arabic":"وَيَمۡنَعُونَ ٱلۡمَاعُونَ","category":["107 (Al-Ma'un)","Al-Ma'un","Surah Al-Ma'un"],"ayahNumber":6204,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"3. आयत संख्या 7 में मामूली चाज़ के लिए 'माऊन' शब्द का प्रयोग हुआ है। जिसका अर्थ है साधारण माँगने के सामान जैसे पानी, आग, नमक, डोल आदि। और आयत का अभिप्राय यह है कि आख़िरत का इनकार किसी व्यक्ति को इतना तंगदिल बना देता है कि वह साधारण उपकार के लिए भी तैयार नहीं होता।","lang":"hi","meta":{"transliteration":"wayamnaʿūna al-māʿūna ","translations":["And they deny","[the] small kindnesses","(7)"],"transliterationArr":["wayamnaʿūna","al-māʿūna",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1500],[2,1500,6525]]}}],"chapter":["107 (Al-Ma'un)","Al-Ma'un","Surah Al-Ma'un","Chapter Al-Ma'un","Ma'un","Surah Ma'un","Chapter Ma'un","Al Ma'un","Surah Al Ma'un","Chapter Al Ma'un","Surah 107","Chapter 107","The Small Kindnesses","الماعون"],"version":{"key":"hindi_omari","direction":"ltr","language_iso_code":"hi","version":"1.1.4","last_update":1675069101,"title":"Hindi Translation","description":"Translation of the Quran meanings into Indian by Azizul-Haqq Al-Umary."}}